    <item>
      <title>日本的收益提升，自动关税担心帽子上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/japan-stocks-fluctuate-amid-concern-over-us-economy-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的更广泛的Topix索引与桑里奥（Sanrio）这样的公司的季度收益超过了预期的季度收益，从而抵消了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的最新评论后，人们对潜在的美国对汽车制造商的关税感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/japan-stocks-fluctuate-amid-concern-over-us-economy-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 00:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
